data.title: LibGuides at CUNY Hunter College
data.meta_description: This guide focuses on resources for researching European History during the Medieval, Early Modern and Modern periods.
data.text:
Det digitale Nasjonalbiblioteket

Digitized collections for the Norwegian National Library includes books, images and other material.

Kansallisarkiston Digitaaliarkisto

Digitized collections of the Finnish National Archive.

Kvinnors kamp för rösträtt

Swedish women's suffrage site includes photographs, documents and other material.

National Library of Finland Digital Collections

Digitized newspapers, ephemera and more.

Project Runeberg

Transcriptions of Scandinavian literary and other works.

Promise of America--Norwegian Emigration to America and Norwegian-American History 1825-2000

Collection includes transcripts of immigrant letters, books and other texts.

SagnaNet

Digitized collection of Icelandic medieval family sagas.

Digiteeritud Eesti Ajalehed

Digitized newspapers dating from 1821 to 1944 from the National Library of Estonia.

Letonica | Latvian National Digital Library

Digitized collection includes newspapers, historic photographs, posters and more.
